<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.8.7">
<l>muḻucivaṇ ṭāṭiya taṇṭuḻāyiṉ moymmalark kaṇṇiyum mēṉiyañcān</l>
<l>tiḻiciya kōlami runtavāṟu meṅṅaṉañ collukē ṉōvinallār</l>
<l>eḻutiya tāmarai yaṉṉakaṇṇu mēnteḻi lākamun tōḷumvāyu</l>
<l>maḻakiya tāmiva rārkkoleṉṉa vaṭṭapu yakarat tēṉeṉṟārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How do I describe the way [his] form is with fine sandalwood powder</l>
<l rend="indent">daubed [on his] body,</l>
<l>And a wreath with masses of flowers of fresh tulasī</l>
<l rend="indent">where bees dive and dance?</l>
<l>When I asked, “Who is this whose eyes, like lotuses drawn by skilled artists,</l>
<l rend="indent">strong, sturdy chest, shoulders, and mouth are beauty [itself]?”</l>
<l>He answered, “I am he in the house of the eight-armed [lord].”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
